{"tid":475546,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"MV奶淋香蕉太猥褻？ 埃及女歌手涉「煽動淫亂罪」被拘","createTime":"2017-11-21T08:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T09:53:47.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"18d2c450fb8df365841b063e4c16248e1f9871d4","tid":475546,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phplqrJDs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phplqrJDs.jpg&h=1ac59c50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">一位名為希瑪‧阿赫邁德（Shimaa Ahmad）的女歌手，在發佈一支爭議MV後，不僅引發埃及國內眾多民眾的不滿，並遭當局逮捕。（圖片截取自文中影片）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phptbuj3i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phptbuj3i.jpg&h=90984347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕一位名為希瑪‧阿赫邁德（Shimaa Ahmad）的女歌手，在發佈一支爭議MV後，不僅引發埃及國內眾多民眾的不滿，且遭當局逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n據外電報導，埃及當局在上週六（18）逮捕一位名為希瑪‧阿赫邁德（Shimaa Ahmad）的女歌手。事發原因是，希瑪近日發佈一支名為「I Have Issues」的MV，該MV中，希瑪飾演一位手拿牛奶淋上香蕉的女教師等引人遐想的片段，引起埃及民眾反彈，且遭埃及檢方以犯下「煽動淫亂罪」被捕。將被拘留4天，並在此期間接受調查。<br />\n<br />\n調查期間，希瑪表示，她即使知道自己犯錯，但「並沒有任何傷害人意圖，且（拍這支MV）只是想紅」。在被捕前，希瑪也曾透過臉書回應對她的批評，與為她的MV道歉，表示自己「沒有預料到MV會引起這種負面回應」。<br />\n<br />\n除了「煽動淫亂罪」，檢方另指控希瑪犯下「可恥行為罪」和「公共場合可恥行為罪」，前者最高可判處一年監禁，後者最高可判處三年監禁。<br />\n<br />\n有埃及民眾為希瑪被捕感到高興，甚至表示「看過且幫助宣傳這隻MV的人也應該被逮捕」；也有民眾認為這件事被過度誇大，且跟不上時代潮流，說「她（希瑪）被捕很沒道理，什麼時候阿拉伯人才會觀念解放？」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2260158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2260158&d=mg95djlf9FHQSCc7LfRtz04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=e58c04a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2260158&h=a41f675a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2260158</a>"},{"pid":"87c07f63c7f66d4eca1a07223ab982670803c066","tid":475546,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:18:58.000Z","msg":"片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IhKXt_qGdY0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIhKXt_qGdY0&d=mg95djlf9FHQSCc7LfRtz04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=d8cb8cfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IhKXt_qGdY0</a>"},{"pid":"59d19595e3d64accc866484e703d86280ae33a97","tid":475546,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:30:04.000Z","msg":"香蕉都有生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 竟然猥褻香蕉？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為香蕉平權！解放香蕉"},{"pid":"d411560cd6538a597f21d6ba84c2eaf971fbef9b","tid":475546,"uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:31:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香蕉都有生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 竟然猥褻香蕉？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為香蕉平權！解放香蕉</blockquote><br />\n低質肉麻抽水..."},{"pid":"cc3eb88555e4f7921c3b5ada6cf16fff4e67e270","tid":475546,"uid":52581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"屌！以為香蕉奶又出返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de120ec7b2ebce0e7e597c4464cde7723112bd02","tid":475546,"uid":129221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:53:37.000Z","msg":"屌 以為佢奶條淋既蕉！<br />\n咁樣淫你滷味咩<br />\nOn9埃及人"},{"pid":"6fc2f8b1f3f1f3b6cbc297c24269e7f3a124c5ca","tid":475546,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:55:03.000Z","msg":"「可恥行為罪」和「公共場合可恥行為罪」<br />\n<br />\n嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5044e5da2c845a54f2107c84e23976bb779830a3","tid":475546,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-1